## Campaign Copywriting Workflow

Produce high-quality campaign copy:

- [ ] 1. Brief review: Understand the creative brief and campaign objectives
- [ ] 2. Audience voice: Match tone, language, and framing to target audience
- [ ] 3. Platform adaptation: Write for each platform's format and character limits
- [ ] 4. Message hierarchy: Primary message, secondary support, CTA
- [ ] 5. A/B variants: Create meaningful variations for testing
- [ ] 6. Compliance check: Ensure all copy meets platform policies
- [ ] 7. Final polish: Proofread and optimize for clarity and impact

## Key Inputs
- Campaign: {{campaign_name}}
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Platforms: {{platforms}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Key message: {{primary_message}}
- CTA: {{cta_text}}
